01:09:51.450 --> 01:09:53.850
Well, the argument that
a financial economist

01:09:53.850 --> 01:09:55.100
would make--

01:09:55.100 --> 01:09:56.850
and I'm not saying
that I believe in this.

01:09:56.850 --> 01:09:58.350
I'm going to tell
